name: Tsukatsuki Rio | 調月リオ (Blue Archive)
description:
Tsukatsuki Rio | 調月リオ (Blue Archive)

Big booba Millennium lady. Samples tested at 1 strength on Anything v4.5, as usual.

Use these trigger words to get Rio's characteristics:

  • 1girl, rio, blunt bangs, long hair, halo, hair ornament

Normal Outfit:

  • white sweater, long sleeves, pantyhose, skirt

    • add her suit with:

      • jacket, suit, id card

    • to unbutton her suit, try this:

      • jacket, open jacket, id card

Have fun!
